    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You cannot increase the runtime to more than 15 minutes.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"http://docs.aws.amazon.com/lambda/latest/dg/limits.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">AWS Lambda <code>limit</code> page</a> states the <code>Function timeout</code> is <code>900 seconds (15 minutes)</code>. If you need more than 15 minutes of execution time you have to look at other services. You could have a look if <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/batch/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">AWS Batch</a> would suit your needs.</p>\n<p><strong>Updated:</strong> The limit was changed from 5 minutes to 15 minutes.</p>\n"
  }, {
