    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Now you can run AWS Lambda up to 15 minutes!</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2018/10/aws-lambda-supports-functions-that-can-run-up-to-15-minutes/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2018/10/aws-lambda-supports-functions-that-can-run-up-to-15-minutes/</a></p>\n"
