    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Of course you can. My solution is:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Track time elapse in your lambda function</li>\n<li>When it about to exceeds the limit, send a notification to SNS topic, then exit.</li>\n<li>Set the SNS topic as trigger to your lambda function.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Keep in mind lambda's original purpose is to run short task so it's better to keep your lambda function run within 15 mins.</p>\n"
